and supported InstallerNG. You can report all incompatibilities.

PS:

InstallWizard uses the amiga port of the unix command sed. The binary of the command
is provided in the package.

SED 2.05:
Uploader <scherer@genesis.informatik.rwth-aachen.de>
Type: util/gnu

This is GNU SED 2.05 for the Commodore Amiga.  The port is based on the
unmodified GNU SED source archive sed-2.05.tar.gz, which is assumed as a
prerequisite, and was done with SAS/C++ 6.55 (no ixemul.library needed).
